@startuml
Campaign_StateMachine

state WaitingForStaffAssignment
state WaitingForApproval
state PreparingAdverts
state SchedulingAdverts
state RunningAdverts
state AdjustingCampaign
state CompletingCampaign
state HandlingPayment
state WaitingForBalanceSettlement
state MarkedAsPaid
state Archived

[*]WaitingForStaffAssignment --> WaitingForApproval
WaitingForApproval --> PreparingAdverts
PreparingAdverts --> SchedulingAdverts
SchedulingAdverts --> RunningAdverts
RunningAdverts --|> AdjustingCampaign
AdjustingCampaign --|> RunningAdverts
RunningAdverts --|> CompletingCampaign
CompletingCampaign --> HandlingPayment
HandlingPayment --|> WaitingForBalanceSettlement
WaitingForBalanceSettlement --|> MarkedAsPaid
MarkedAsPaid --> Archived
@enduml
